com.socrata.builders

Class AbstractDatasetInfoBuilder<BUILDER extends AbstractDatasetInfoBuilder,BUILDEE extends DatasetInfo>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.socrata.builders.AbstractDatasetInfoBuilder<BUILDER,BUILDEE>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DatasetBuilder, DatasetInfoBuilder, ExternalDatasetBuilder, NonDataFileDatasetBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractDatasetInfoBuilder<BUILDER extends AbstractDatasetInfoBuilder,BUILDEE extends DatasetInfo>
extends Object
    A DatasetInfoBuilder that can be used by builders of all the sub-classes. Handles all the common properties.

        public void populate(DatasetInfo retVal)

        Parameters:
